      "content": "i get that, but he's really insistent that he just needs to sleep it off. he's even saying his face feels a little different too, but he thinks it's just from sleeping in a weird position on the plane. if we just gave him some electrolytes and let him nap for a few hours, would that be okay? he really doesn't want to deal with an ER visit if it's just travel stress.",
